Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.40,0:00:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh... if you're looking for that mansion...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.82,0:00:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just keep going up this hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.82,0:00:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.16,0:00:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.94,0:00:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roses...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.10,0:00:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This almost seems like Sleeping Beauty's castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.54,0:02:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My name is Anna... Anna Liebert.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.96,0:02:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Good luck, Mr. Detective.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.22,0:02:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If something were to happen to you...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.13,0:02:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I think of that..{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.05,0:02:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.64,0:02:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I feel the same way your mother did, so...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.56,0:02:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anna...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.77,0:02:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you dreaming...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.48,0:02:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Detective Suk?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.53,0:02:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.44,0:02:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.65,0:02:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lunge.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.32,0:02:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An inspector from the German BKA.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.28,0:02:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,BKA?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.74,0:02:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.99,0:02:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to sit up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.83,0:02:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't come here to arrest you or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.30,0:03:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a pretty nice hospital room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.34,0:03:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The old Czechoslovakian secret police...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.93,0:03:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I traced all the hospitals they were connected to...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.72,0:03:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and finally ended up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.68,0:03:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think you're receiving such treatment...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.10,0:03:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from the old Czechoslovakian secret police...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.60,0:03:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be important to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.60,0:03:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm just...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.56,0:03:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already know what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.98,0:03:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know about Inspector Zeman's connection\Nto the secret police and his brutal death.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.49,0:03:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prague's police chief and two officers\Nwere poisoned to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.66,0:03:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The two agents who were sent to tail you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.04,0:03:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,were found shot to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.67,0:03:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're the chief suspect in all the\Nincidents that have taken place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.22,0:03:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Considering all the evidence stacked against you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.18,0:03:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you're the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.80,0:03:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.01,0:03:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.64,0:03:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then could it be Grimmer, the tall, thin man...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.73,0:03:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who was talking with Inspector Zeman\Nthe day before he was killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.23,0:03:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not Mr. Grimmer, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.06,0:04:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wouldn't do something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.94,0:04:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, who is the killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.11,0:04:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.91,0:04:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know who the killer is right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.83,0:04:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.50,0:04:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I knew, I wouldn't be in this state.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.79,0:04:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deceived by so many people...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.96,0:04:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,set up to take the fall...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.17,0:04:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even being on the run from the police...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.01,0:04:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've had enough of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.97,0:04:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be betrayed anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.60,0:04:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a detective, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.60,0:04:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're a detective...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.98,0:04:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then you have to calmly dissect the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.07,0:04:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's painful...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.99,0:04:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you must calmly uncover the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.99,0:04:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want to be betrayed anymore...\
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.87,0:05:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then start doubting the person\Nyou want to doubt the least.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.68,0:05:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who gave you permission to see him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.40,0:05:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see your boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.94,0:05:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell him I want to speak with him about the Rose Mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.28,0:05:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll want to meet with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.55,0:05:34.85,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(330,0)\pos(364,353)}The Rose Mansion
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.20,0:05:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector Lunge from the German BKA.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.33,0:05:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm familiar with your background and personal history.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.04,0:05:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've also heard rumors about you since the old regime...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.80,0:05:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Colonel Ranke.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.21,0:05:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now you're practically the head of\Nthe old Czechoslovakian secret police.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.89,0:05:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it must be quite difficult to control such\Na large organization these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.81,0:05:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.85,0:06:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm envious that you're able to take\Nsuch an extended vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.23,0:06:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two years ago, the secretary for Senator Borzmann,\Nthe German Democratic Party candidate...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.70,0:06:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,committed suicide due to your thorough investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.91,0:06:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be a little smarter in what you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.12,0:06:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the fool here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.46,0:06:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you seemed legitimate on the surface...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.75,0:06:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you could have secretly run this country...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.96,0:06:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and acted as the president from the shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.84,0:06:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now, the frightened citizens see you as you really are.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.23,0:06:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.40,0:06:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a smart one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.52,0:06:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what does a smart man like you want from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.78,0:06:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, as you know, I'm not simply on\Nthis extended vacation for leisure...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.49,0:06:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been searching...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.20,0:07:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for the existence of true terror.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.83,0:07:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a possibility that the illusion you created...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.59,0:07:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,may have given birth to the devil itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.80,0:07:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is about the Red Rose Mansion?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.73,0:07:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had to investigate quite a bit\N\Nbefore I found the mansion...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.06,0:07:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because the author has so many pen names.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.11,0:07:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Monster Without a Name. "
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.11,0:07:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By Emil Sebe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.91,0:07:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Address, an office in an old building in Prague.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.16,0:07:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, another company is leasing the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.70,0:07:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Klaus Poppe's address was listed as\Nan old farmhouse outside the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.71,0:07:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was demolished.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.25,0:07:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jakov Vyrobek's was just a rented office, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.26,0:07:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.22,0:07:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,did you find him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.89,0:07:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franz Bonaparta?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.76,0:08:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that mansion?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.19,0:08:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And who is Franz Bonaparta?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.15,0:08:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every search I run on him comes up with nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.65,0:08:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means he must be under your protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.62,0:08:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An old Czechoslovakian secret police officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.54,0:08:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.96,0:08:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know what you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.75,0:08:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.92,0:08:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.13,0:08:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.26,0:08:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been consciously trying to forget...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.97,0:08:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that the mansion ever existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.31,0:08:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I never did anything about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.90,0:08:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and it's still there, untouched.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.52,0:08:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that mansion...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.61,0:08:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all the political prisoners and researchers\Nheld there vanished one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.53,0:09:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.12,0:09:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that wall for?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.04,0:09:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wall?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.50,0:09:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was inside the mansion a few days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.22,0:09:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was no sign that anyone else\Nhad recently been in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.68,0:09:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was completely abandoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.76,0:09:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.01,0:09:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the north wall on the second floor...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.60,0:09:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was built rather hastily, as if to hide something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.69,0:09:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May I break down that wall?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.62,0:09:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you afraid of, Colonel Ranke?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.41,0:09:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may die.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.00,0:09:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we come any closer...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.38,0:10:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we may come face to face with true terror!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.79,0:11:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franz Bonaparta...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.63,0:11:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a nostalgic name.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.38,0:11:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want cream and sugar in your coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.59,0:11:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, black is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.18,0:12:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.64,0:12:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.85,0:12:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just surprising to have a fan of\NFranz Bonaparta come here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.48,0:12:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got your address from Moravia Publishing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.19,0:12:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Sovak, you were Bonaparta's editor\Nwhen he was still writing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.66,0:12:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.91,0:12:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was only his editor when he was\Ngoing by the pen name Klaus Poppe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.87,0:12:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mind telling me what he was like?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.67,0:12:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franz Bonaparta?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.75,0:12:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He used to have his work-related\Nmeetings here in this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.47,0:12:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he used to sit in that chair, just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.69,0:12:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He would often play with my daughter in the yard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.65,0:12:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, my daughter said something rather strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.40,0:12:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"That man is .scary."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.53,0:13:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My daughter was still little at the time, so she\Nprobably doesn't remember anything now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.50,0:13:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was he working with the government back then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.59,0:13:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.00,0:13:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I associated with him assuming that he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.67,0:13:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, his mannerisms, his way of speaking...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.22,0:13:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the clothes he wore, were all unlike other\Ngovernment VIPs under the old regime.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.56,0:13:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he had a gentleness and elegance about him...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.98,0:13:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bonaparta had a master's in psychology\Nand was a practicing psychologist.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.44,0:13:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was also a medical doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.86,0:13:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His specialty was brain surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.19,0:13:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.16,0:13:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The last time I saw him was... let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.53,0:13:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it was the summer of '81 or '82.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.58,0:13:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he just suddenly showed up at my house one day...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.62,0:13:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with a new story...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.00,0:13:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He looked somewhat refreshed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.63,0:13:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A new story...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.05,0:13:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of story was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.68,0:14:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A story about a monster falling in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.77,0:14:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it was like a combination of "Beauty\Nand the Beast" and "Sleeping Beauty."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.65,0:14:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I rejected it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.57,0:14:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, in the doorway just before he left...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.15,0:14:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he turned around and said, "How about this one?"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.12,0:14:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Door That Must Never Be Opened."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.33,0:14:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I asked him...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.37,0:14:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"So, on the other side of the door do you find paradise..."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.13,0:14:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"or a monster biding its time?"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.75,0:14:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he said...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.63,0:14:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Since the door must never be opened, there's no story..."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.01,0:14:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He laughed, and left.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.26,0:14:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the last time I saw him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.23,0:15:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, did you learn anything about Bonaparta?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.07,0:15:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.28,0:15:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Grimmer, why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.71,0:15:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just thinking what a fine day it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.63,0:15:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.59,0:15:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.59,0:15:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, is this the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.84,0:15:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Sovak, I live on Svejk Court.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.56,0:15:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The guy that just visited me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.06,0:15:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.93,0:15:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think he's wanted for a series of murders in Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.94,0:15:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he's Japanese... a brain surgeon named Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.58,0:15:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ethanol...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.42,0:15:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This room reeks of antiseptics.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.70,0:16:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.15,0:16:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.78,0:16:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many people died here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.24,0:16:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.41,0:16:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Twenty...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.66,0:16:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, more than that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.06,0:16:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.44,0:17:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The woman from the sketchbook.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.11,0:17:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she the mother of the twins?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.54,0:17:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't hurry, the older kids will take the soccer field.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.87,0:17:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up, Milos!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.54,0:17:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.13,0:17:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Counterattack!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.25,0:17:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! Fall back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.46,0:17:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The goal is wide open!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.38,0:17:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... he's gonna score!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.05,0:17:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Milos!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.85,0:17:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Milos?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.31,0:17:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there, Milos.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.35,0:17:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice defense, Milos!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.23,0:17:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.40,0:17:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You saved a goal!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.91,0:17:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the way he's laughing...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.57,0:17:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he should be all right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.79,0:17:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.04,0:17:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.21,0:18:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Grimmer...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.34,0:18:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,aren't you going to see Milos and the other boys?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.43,0:18:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand now why I'm bad at soccer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.64,0:18:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about teamwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.85,0:18:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going to happen to Detective Jan Suk now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.27,0:18:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the prime suspect in this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.82,0:18:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same thing as being socially blacklisted.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.99,0:18:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he turns himself in...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.91,0:18:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,how can we prove his innocence?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.87,0:18:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can we show that the blonde\Ngirl left the crime scene?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.38,0:18:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suk must be in the same predicament you're in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.34,0:18:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, there is one thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.34,0:18:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.80,0:18:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.18,0:18:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Regarding this case...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.60,0:19:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's only one person who knows all the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.69,0:19:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.07,0:19:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.82,0:19:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I hand this over to the police...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.66,0:19:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.32,0:19:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A letter from the serial killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.75,0:19:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Details that only the killer would know...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.71,0:19:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,would make a convincing confession, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.38,0:19:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you send this to the police, you'll be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.72,0:19:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grimmer returned to Germany before you even knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.80,0:19:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NEven though the police will try to catch him, Grimmer\Nis capable of staying out of their reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.39,0:19:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because he used to be an elite spy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.27,0:19:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you'll be a suspect for the rest of your\Nlife, and will always be on the run...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.90,0:19:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.40,0:19:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because the man named Grimmer\Nnever existed in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.87,0:20:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone gave him that name out of convenience.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.04,0:20:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if Grimmer is a suspect for the rest of his life...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.92,0:20:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it'd be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.13,0:20:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.13,0:20:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Tenma, what do you think of the decision I made?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.26,0:20:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh... never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.22,0:20:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.26,0:20:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're heading to the Rose Mansion now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.81,0:20:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.93,0:20:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may finally be getting close to your goal, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.69,0:20:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.02,0:20:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I tell you not to be reckless,\Nit won't change anything, will it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.03,0:20:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.82,0:20:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,don't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.20,0:20:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Grimmer...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.12,0:20:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The promise we made when we\Ncrossed the Czech border...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.42,0:20:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That if we met again, we'd have another picnic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.80,0:20:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fishing for rainbow trout, surrounded\Nby beautiful scenery...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.72,0:20:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,having good wine with good cheese...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.05,0:20:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll do that again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.83,0:21:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always be living in fear of that sound from here on out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.79,0:21:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.21,0:21:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch! It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.92,0:21:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.06,0:21:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.31,0:21:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me take a look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.56,0:21:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.77,0:21:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.90,0:21:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put some antiseptic on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.32,0:21:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.36,0:22:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a boy, bear with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.08,0:22:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.99,0:22:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a strong kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.79,0:22:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenzou Tenma, I presume...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.42,0:22:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.84,0:22:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd like you to come with us...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.77,0:22:30.94,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(170,472)}Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.94,0:22:44.37,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(200,474)}Cherish what you know is true in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.94,0:22:44.37,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(196,21)}Ima kono sekai de wakaru koto mitsumete
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.37,0:22:47.33,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(182,472)}Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.33,0:23:01.01,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(198,472)}Please believe in the kindness of your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.33,0:23:01.01,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(193,21)}Anata no hitomi no yasashisa wo shinjite
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.61,0:23:25.87,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(196,473)}Make it home to your land of harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.87,0:23:34.29,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(195,473)}Make it home to your land of purity
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.29,0:23:36.75,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,246)\pos(187,472)}Make it home
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.85,0:23:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
